---
// Side-by-side: bad vs good buck converter hot-loop layout.
---
<div class="not-prose grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rose-700">BAD — 큰 핫 루프</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="178" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />
      <!-- Cin (far) -->
      <rect x="20" y="40" width="22" height="35" fill="#0ea5e9" stroke="#075985" />
      <text x="20" y="36" font-size="9" fill="#075985" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Cin</text>
      <!-- IC -->
      <rect x="120" y="60" width="60" height="50" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="135" y="90" font-size="10" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">DCDC</text>
      <!-- Inductor -->
      <rect x="200" y="70" width="36" height="14" fill="#fbbf24" stroke="#92400e" />
      <text x="200" y="64" font-size="9" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">L</text>
      <!-- Cout -->
      <rect x="260" y="65" width="22" height="35" fill="#10b981" stroke="#047857" />
      <text x="258" y="58" font-size="9" fill="#047857" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Cout</text>

      <!-- Bad routing: Cin far from IC, big return loop -->
      <line x1="42" y1="58" x2="120" y2="70" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2" />
      <line x1="42" y1="73" x2="120" y2="100" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
      <text x="58" y="115" font-size="9" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">긴 루프 = 큰 di/dt 노이즈</text>

      <!-- Highlight loop area -->
      <path d="M 42 58 L 120 70 L 120 110 L 42 75 Z" fill="#fecaca" opacity="0.5" />
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-rose-800">Cin 이 IC 에서 멀리 떨어져 핫 루프 면적이 크다 → di/dt × L<sub>loop</sub> 만큼 스파이크 → EMI</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-700">GOOD — Cin 이 핀 바로 옆</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="178" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />
      <!-- IC -->
      <rect x="120" y="60" width="60" height="50" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="135" y="90" font-size="10" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">DCDC</text>
      <!-- Cin tight to IC -->
      <rect x="100" y="65" width="18" height="22" fill="#0ea5e9" stroke="#075985" />
      <text x="98" y="60" font-size="9" fill="#075985" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Cin</text>
      <!-- Inductor -->
      <rect x="200" y="70" width="36" height="14" fill="#fbbf24" stroke="#92400e" />
      <text x="200" y="64" font-size="9" fill="#92400e" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">L</text>
      <!-- Cout -->
      <rect x="260" y="65" width="22" height="35" fill="#10b981" stroke="#047857" />
      <text x="258" y="58" font-size="9" fill="#047857" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Cout</text>

      <!-- Tight loop -->
      <line x1="118" y1="70" x2="120" y2="70" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" />
      <line x1="118" y1="87" x2="120" y2="100" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
      <path d="M 118 70 L 120 70 L 120 110 L 118 87 Z" fill="#bbf7d0" opacity="0.5" />

      <!-- GND plane below -->
      <rect x="20" y="135" width="280" height="14" fill="#94a3b8" stroke="#64748b" />
      <text x="22" y="146" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">GND plane (인접 층)</text>
      <line x1="135" y1="110" x2="135" y2="135" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="1.4" />
      <text x="138" y="128" font-size="9" fill="#047857" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">via drop</text>
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-emerald-800">Cin 핀 바로 옆 → 핫 루프 mm 단위 → di/dt × L 작아 EMI 무난.</figcaption>
  </figure>
</div>
